parameters: Now is not the time to go back, let's head east.

\nw[Kuno]Wait at this point. We still have some time until
the scheduled time, but what should we do?

\nw[Kuno]Marriage, huh... Hehe, there have been various
things.
\nw[Taro]I don't think we need to rush that much.

\nw[Kuno]We talked about it properly, didn't we? We've
already made a decision, so let's not bring that
up, okay?

\nw[Kuno]Just like my parents and Taro's parents, we don't
know what might happen...

\nw[Taro](We still have some time, so how about we do
something romantic as a couple...?)

\nw[Taro](No, this isn't the right atmosphere, and it would
be weird to suddenly kiss...)

\nw[Kuno]Is that so? It might start earlier than planned,
so we have to keep a close watch.

\nw[Taro](To begin with, we've never really done anything
couple-like until now...)

\nw[Kuno]I hear the sounds of battle... It seems like it
has begun.

\nw[Kuno]I'll keep watch to see if anyone comes running
here.

\nw[Taro]Well, I guess that's how it goes. We have to stay
alert until we receive confirmation that the
operation is over.
\nw[Kuno]Yes, if we let our guard down...

\nw[Taro]Why am I in a place like this...? Aegis refers to
the strongest ten soldiers of the Misura Kingdom,
right?

\nw[Taro]Even though we're near the border between Dios and
Misura, there's no reason for thieves from the
Dios side to come out...

\nw[Kuno]I don't care about that!... I will never forgive
you!

\nw[Taro]Let's go, Kuno! It seems like we can go from the
east!

This is our destination. If we go further, we
might be found by thieves, so let's stop here.
